---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { getLatestRelease } from "../lib/github";

const release = await getLatestRelease();
const tagName = release.tag_name;
---

<Layout title="ShowDraw - OBS線画強調プラグイン" lang="ja">
  <h1>手元の線画、もっとクリアに視聴者へ。</h1>
  <p>
    ShowDrawは、アナログイラスト配信のためのOBS
    Studioプラグインです。カメラに映る繊細な線をリアルタイムでくっきりと強調し、あなたの創作過程を視聴者と鮮明に共有できます。
  </p>
  <p lang="en">
    Showcase your analog line art, clearer than ever. ShowDraw is an OBS Studio
    plugin for illustrators that enhances your hand-drawn lines in real-time,
    allowing you to share every delicate stroke with your viewers.
  </p>
  <div class="links">
    <a href="/plugin-description/ja/">日本語で詳しく見る</a>
    <a href="/plugin-description/en/">Learn more in English</a>
  </div>
  <div class="links">
    <a
      href=`https://github.com/kaito-tokyo/obs-showdraw/releases/download/${tagName}/obs-showdraw-${tagName}-windows-x64.zip`
      >Windows</a
    >
    <a
      href=`https://github.com/kaito-tokyo/obs-showdraw/releases/download/${tagName}/obs-showdraw-${tagName}-macos-universal.pkg`
      >Mac</a
    >
    <a
      href=`https://github.com/kaito-tokyo/obs-showdraw/releases/download/${tagName}/obs-showdraw-${tagName}-x86_64-linux-gnu.deb`
      >Ubuntu</a
    >
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    margin: auto;
    padding: 1rem;
    width: 800px;
    max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
    color: black;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1em;
  }
  .links {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 2em;
  }
  .links a {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    background-color: #4caf50; /* Green */
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 18px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }
  .links a:hover {
    background-color: #45a049;
  }
</style>
